OL,3,CElectrician has tools worth thousands
OL,4,Cstolen leaving him unable to work
OL,6,FAn electrician from Poole has been
OL,7,Fleft thousands of pounds out of pocket
OL,8,Fafter thieves stole tools from his van.
OL,10,FSimon Blackmore woke to find his van
OL,11,Fdoor ajar and nearly all of his kit
OL,12,Fgone.
OL,14,FHe's had to postpone jobs whilst he
OL,15,Ffound replacement tools, impacting his
OL,16,Fbusiness and delaying important work.
OL,18,FSimon says it's the second time he's
OL,19,Fbeen targeted. Previously one of his
OL,20,Fvans was targeted in broad daylight.
