OL,6,FFigures from Direct Line released in
OL,7,FJune show 62% of tradespeople had
OL,8,Ftools stolen from their vans.
OL,10,FSimon contacted Dorset Police who say
OL,11,Fthey are investigating.
OL,13,FThe force told us that the decision to
OL,14,Fsend officers to the scene of a crime
OL,15,Fis based on the threat level at the
OL,16,Ftime and resources are prioritised
OL,17,Fwhere they can be most effective.
