OL,6,FIn a statement they said: "Dorset
OL,7,FPolice received a report at 7.10am on
OL,8,FThursday 8 August relating to the
OL,9,Ftheft of tools from a vehicle in
OL,10,FBrampton Road in Poole.
OL,12,F"Officers will be carrying out a
OL,13,Freview of all available lines of
OL,14,Fenquiry and carrying out an
OL,15,Fappropriate investigation.
OL,17,F"We recognise the impact crimes of
OL,18,Fthis nature have on victims and we
OL,19,Fremain committed to exploring all
OL,20,Favailable lines of enquiry to identify
OL,21,Fthose involved."
